stop the car and pull over
then you take a look which tire hase been flat
you open your trunk
take out the equipments that you need
the take out the jack
put it under the car
lift the car up by the side
bring the wrench
open the lug nuts
then you bring the spare tire
replace it with the old tire
then you put back the lug nuts
bring the car down
remove the jack
put everything in trunk
go seat inside the car
fasten your seatbelt
